race.description: Independent Liquor Group Publicans Cup F
race.comment: APACHE TIGER (2) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by half a length (29.39). Looks a top chance again. WHISKEY MCGRAW (8) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Placed last time (29.42) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten half a length. Looks well placed here and among the chances. BAD AND BERTHA (7) is a well performed dog who recorded her 9th career win last time out at this track (29.76). Has never been out of the money in five starts this course and distance. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. One of the leading chances again. HIGHWAY PRINCESS (1) warrants respect following a recent placing.
